                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="img-out-text">
                                <p>Through her webseries, <b>Pardon My <br/> French,</b> Garance covers fashion, beauty, <br/> travel, and lifestyle and travel with her <br/> unique point-of-view</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div> <!-- /.row -->

                    <div class="row">
                        <div id="rent4" class="rent col-md-4">
                            <div class="img-container">
                                <img src="{{ asset('images/home/rent4.jpg') }}">
                                <div class="img-in-text">
                                    <a href="" >FEATURED ACCESSORY</a>
                                    <h1 class="text-center"> Handbags </h1>
                                </div>                                
                            </div>  
                            <div class="img-out-text">
                                <p>An iconic collection of handbags and <br/> jewellry representing contemporary <br/> fashion trends. </p>
                            </div>                              
                        </div>
                        <div id="rent5" class="rent col-md-8">
                            <div class="img-container">
                                <img src="{{ asset('images/home/rent5.png') }}">
